quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"Ndipo pamene mwana wamwamuna wa Maria atchulidwa ngati chitsanzo, taona! Anthu ako amaseka"
  43,58,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Kodi milungu yathu ndiyo yopambana kapena iyeyo ndiye wopambana?” Izi amangozinena kwa iwe ndi cholinga chofuna mikangano ndipo iwo ndi anthu amwano"
  43,59,"Iye sadali wina koma kapolo wathu amene tidamulangiza chisomo chathu, ndipo tidamupanga Iye kukhala chitsanzo kwa ana a Israyeli"
  43,60,Ndipo tikadafuna tikadapanga ena a inu kukhala angelo kuti akhale padziko m’malo mwanu
  43,61,"Ndithudi ichi ndi chizindikiro cha ola, kotero musakayike za ilo ndipo nditsateni ine. Iyo ndiyo njira yoyenera"
  43,62,"Ndipo musalole kuti Satana akutchinjirizeni chifukwa, ndithudi, iye ndi mdani wanu weniweni"
  43,63,"Pamene Yesu adadza ndi zizindikiro zooneka adati, “Tsopano ndadza kwa inu ndi luntha ndi cholinga chokuuzani tsatanetsatane za fundo zina zimene mumatsutsana. Motero opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”"
  43,64,“Ndithudi Mulungu! Ndiye Ambuye wanga ndi Ambuye wanu. Motero mutumikireni Iye. Imeneyi ndiyo njira yoyenera.”
  43,65,"Koma magulu ena a pakati pawo adapatukana, kotero tsoka kwa iwo amene adali oipa chifukwa cha chilango chowawa chimene chidzadza pa iwo patsiku la masautso"
  43,66,Kodi iwo ali kungodikira kuti ola lidzadza pa iwo mwadzidzidzi pamene iwo sali kudziwa
  43,67,Abwenzi patsiku limeneli adzasanduka adani kupatula okhawo amene amalewa zoipa